  rdf:type schema:Article ;
  schema:url &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/engineering/domains/domesticity/domains/production/gardening/terms/bloody-dock/> ;
  schema:name "Bloody dock cultivation" ;
  schema:description "Growing protocol for *Rumex sanguineus*, perennial herb producing deep-red-veined foliage and lemony, sour flavor from oxalic acid. Establish from seed; produces harvestable rosette in first year. Longevous perennial (zone 4+); allows multiple harvests per season without replanting. Ornamental foliage value in mixed borders." ;
